" # VIM SETTINGS
" #
" # REFERENCES:
" #   https://github.com/mhinz/vim-galore/blob/master/static/minimal-vimrc.vim
" #   http://ivanbrennan.nyc/blog/2014/01/16/rigging-vims-netrw/
